StartDICOMImportJob.name: StartDICOMImportJob
StartDICOMImportJob.documentation: Start importing bulk data into an active data store. The import job will import DICOM P10 files found in the S3 prefix specified by the inputS3Uri parameter. The results of the output job will be stored in the file specified by the outputS3Uri parameter.

documentation:
This is the Amazon HealthLake Imaging API Reference. HealthLake Imaging is an AWS service for storing, accessing, and managing medical images. For an introduction to the service, see the Amazon HealthLake Imaging Developer Guide.

We recommend using one of the AWS Software Development Kits (SDKs) for your programming language, as they take care of request authentication, serialization, and connection management. For more information, see Tools to build on AWS.
